member.example:
This sample shows how to call RemoveConnectionFromAllGroupsAsync with required parameters.

var client = new WebPubSubClient("<https://my-service.azure.com>");

Response response = await client.RemoveConnectionFromAllGroupsAsync("<hub>", "<connectionId>");
Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

